<item>
            <title>[LU-11296] page cache cleanup improvement on lock flush</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11296</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If client A writes a 100 GiB file, then client B attempts to read it, the cached PW lock on client A will be flushed together with page cache data. It can take 5-10 s just to complete that.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can speed up cache invalidation a bit.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
